'''土著權威組織'''（{{lang-ms|Persatuan Pribumi Perkasa}}，簡稱{{lang|ms|Perkasa}}），是[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]一個提倡[[馬來人至上|馬來人至上]]的非政府組織<ref>{{cite news |title=Perkasa winning support for attacks on demands by minority groups |url=http://www.malaysia-today.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=30138:perkasa-winning-support-for-attacks-on-demands-by-minority-groups&catid=19:newscommentaries&Itemid=100131 |publisher=Malaysia Today |date=2010-02-11 |accessdate=2010-07-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100325222127/http://www.malaysia-today.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=30138%3Aperkasa-winning-support-for-attacks-on-demands-by-minority-groups&catid=19%3Anewscommentaries&Itemid=100131 |archivedate=2010-03-25 }}</ref>，由[[依布拉欣阿里|依布拉欣阿里]]在[[2008年馬來西亞大選|2008年大選]]後成立並擔任主席。2014年時，土著權威組織聲稱其成員人數達42萬人<ref>{{cite news |title=Perkasa poised for a new role |url=http://www.thestar.com.my/Opinion/Columnists/Analysis/Profile/Articles/2014/01/05/Perkasa-poised-for-a-new-role/ |publisher=The Star Online |date=2014-01-05 |accessdate=2014-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140123100136/http://www.thestar.com.my/Opinion/Columnists/Analysis/Profile/Articles/2014/01/05/Perkasa-poised-for-a-new-role/ |archive-date=2014-01-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2010年9月，依布拉欣阿里表示60%的土著權威組織成員均為[[巫統|巫統]]黨員<ref name=UMNOties>{{cite news|title=Perkasa has nothing to do with Umno: Ibrahim Ali|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/story/?file=%2f2010%2f9%2f9%2fnation%2f20100909174045&sec=nation|accessdate=2015-10-15|publisher=The Star (Malaysia)|date=2010-09-09|quote=Ibrahim claimed that 60% of its members were Umno members while its younger members were not politically-affiliated. Perkasa brushed off Umno’s statement that the largest component party in the Barisan Nasional neither needs nor has ties with Perkasa. “We have no ties to sever with Umno as we do not have ties in the first place,” its founder Datuk Ibrahim Ali said.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225171048/http://www.thestar.com.my/story/?file=%2f2010%2f9%2f9%2fnation%2f20100909174045&sec=nation|archive-date=2015-12-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。但是，依布拉欣阿里和巫統秘書長[[東姑安南|東姑安南]]只承認部份巫統黨員是土著權威組織成員<ref>{{cite news|last1=Zuhrin|first1=Azam Ahmad|title=UMNO rejects Perkasa|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/story/?file=%2f2010%2f9%2f9%2fnation%2f7006976&sec=nation|accessdate=2015-10-15|publisher=The Star (Malaysia)|date=2010-09-09|quote=Tengku Adnan said that most Perkasa leaders were defeated in the last Umno elections and had sought a political platform for them to be heard. “They are not wanted in Umno, they are no more leaders, they are just ordinary members. Umno has nothing to do with Perkasa,” he said, adding that the party would not back Ibrahim in the next general election.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227002158/http://www.thestar.com.my/story/?file=%2f2010%2f9%2f9%2fnation%2f7006976&sec=nation|archive-date=2015-12-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Koh|first1=Lay Chin|title=UMNO's Perkasa dilemma|url=http://www.thenutgraph.com/umno%E2%80%99s-perkasa-dilemma/|accessdate=2015-10-15|publisher=The Nut Graph|date=2010-09-20|quote=Tengku Adnan reminded Perkasa leaders that BN had to address the needs of all racial groups in the country. In response, Ibrahim snapped back, saying that 60% of Perkasa members were Umno members. He is also mulling the possibility of political cooperation with other parties in the next election.(Source: Umno rejects Perkasa, The Star, 9 Sept 2010)|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212080449/http://www.thenutgraph.com/umno%E2%80%99s-perkasa-dilemma/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，否認兩者有聯繫<ref name=UMNOties/>。

據依布拉欣阿里表示，成立土著權威組織的目的在於保護《[[馬來西亞憲法|馬來西亞憲法]]》第153條，並捍衛土著權益免被某方面侵蝕<ref>{{cite news |title=The Real Deal with Perkasa |url=http://www.thenutgraph.com/real-deal-perkasa/ |publisher=The Nut Graph |date=2010-03-16 |accessdate=2010-07-29 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021213137/https://thenutgraph.com/real-deal-perkasa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。土著權威組織被認為是為感覺自己的權益被非馬來人挑戰的馬來人爭取和捍衛權益。

土著權威組織因對非馬來人（尤其是[[馬來西亞華人|華人]]和[[馬來西亞印度人|印度人]]）和非穆斯林（尤其是基督徒）以責罵、動武及暴力的方式進行種族及宗教挑釁而為人所知<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2012/05/10/perkasa-antics-will-cost-bn/ |title=Perkasa antics will cost BN |access-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418232550/http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2012/05/10/perkasa-antics-will-cost-bn/ |archive-date=2016-04-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。雖然土著權威組織成員持續煽動性言論對社會和諧構成威脅，但馬來西亞政府並沒有對此作出法律行動<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mmail.com.my/story/call-action-against-perkasa-chief-45041 |title=Call for action against Perkasa chief |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130221033309/http://www.mmail.com.my/story/call-action-against-perkasa-chief-45041 |archivedate=2013-02-21 |accessdate=2016-08-09 }}</ref>。

馬來西亞反對黨聯盟[[人民聯盟_(馬來西亞)|人民聯盟]]形容土著權威組織是一個[[法西斯主義|法西斯主義]]組織<ref>{{cite news |title=Curb "fascist" Perkasa, Rahim Noor, Pakatan MPs tell Najib |url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/curb-fascist-perkasa-rahim-noor-pakatan-mps-tell-najib/ |publisher=The Malaysian Insider |date=2011-10-28 |accessdate=2011-10-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028195139/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/curb-fascist-perkasa-rahim-noor-pakatan-mps-tell-najib/ |archivedate=2011-10-28 }}</ref>。雖然大部份土著權威組織成員均是巫統黨員，依布拉欣阿里表示會探討土著權威組織註冊成為政黨的可能性，並表示有意參加[[2018年马来西亚大选|2018年大選]]以挑戰巫統。依布拉欣阿里在土著權威組織第四次年度大會指控巫統在保衛馬來人利益時軟弱<ref>{{cite news |title=We can replace you as Malay champions Perkasa warns UMNO |url=http://m.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/we-can-replace-you-as-malay-champions-perkasa-warns-umno |publisher=The Malay Mail Online |date=2013-12-22 |accessdate=2014-01-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210849/http://m.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/we-can-replace-you-as-malay-champions-perkasa-warns-umno |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 領導層 ==
前馬來西亞國會議員依布拉欣阿里是土著權威組織的創辦人兼主席。

== 爭議 ==

===發表煽动性文章===
2010年7月1日，土著權威組織的官方報章《土權之聲》在其首頁刊登一篇要求根據《[[马来西亚内安法令|马来西亚内安法令]]》拘押[[馬來西亞華人公會|馬華公會]]青年團總團長[[魏家祥|魏家祥]]的文章，指他質問土著特權違反《馬來西亞憲法》第153條，但魏家祥反駁指控<ref>{{cite news|title= Perkasa: Arrest Ka Siong under ISA|url= http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2010/7/1/nation/6585279&sec=nation|publisher= The Star (Malaysia)|date= 2010-07-01|accessdate= 2010-07-29|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100704032933/http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2010%2F7%2F1%2Fnation%2F6585279&sec=nation|archivedate= 2010-07-04}}</ref>。翌日，《土權之聲》被[[馬來西亞內政部|馬來西亞內政部]]傳召，要求解釋。《土權之聲》的文章引起[[國民陣線_(馬來西亞)|國民陣線]]成員黨巫統、馬華和[[马来西亚印度国民大会党|國大黨]]的反彈<ref>{{cite news|title= Suara Perkasa asked to explain 'ISA' article|url= http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2010/7/2/nation/20100702203845&sec=nation|publisher= The Star (Malaysia)|date= 2010-07-02|accessdate= 2010-07-29|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100705095913/http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2010%2F7%2F2%2Fnation%2F20100702203845&sec=nation|archivedate= 2010-07-05}}</ref>。

===反净选盟2.0遊行===
2011年6月19日，土著權威組織舉行反[[2011年净选盟2.0人民集会|净选盟2.0]]遊行。其主席依布拉欣阿里發表演說時，表示若净选盟2.0集會沒有取消，會發生類似[[五一三事件_(马来西亚)|五一三事件]]的種族衝突，故警告華人需要儲備糧食以作不時之需。此外，他又提醒華人在同年7月9日净选盟2.0集會當天留在室內地方，以免招惹麻煩。其演說引致朝野雙方的國會議員指責，認為他將爭取自由及公平選舉訴求的集會描繪成種族議題。巫統青年團團長[[凱里·嘉馬魯丁|凱里·嘉馬魯丁]]認為應該根據《[[1948年煽動法令|1948年煽動法令]]》，對依布拉欣阿里進行調查<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-claims-chinese-support-in-anti-bersih-drive|title=Perkasa Claims Chinese Support in anti-Bersih drive|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107082833/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-claims-chinese-support-in-anti-bersih-drive|archivedate=2014-01-07|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

===派發白包事件===
在2012年2月土著權威組織舉辦的[[農曆新年|農曆新年]]慶祝活動中，土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里被指向華裔年長公民派發內含1萬令吉的白包。由於白包被華人社會用作包裹帛金，此舉引發馬來西亞華人的不滿。馬來西亞華人領袖形容依布拉欣阿里的舉動是對華人的「不尊重」和「麻木不仁」。依布拉欣阿里其後對事件表示遺憾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2012/1/31/nation/10566887&sec=nation|title=Young MCA leaders see red over Perkasa’s white packets|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502071722/http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2012%2F1%2F31%2Fnation%2F10566887&sec=nation|archivedate=2012-05-02|accessdate=2017-09-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2012/2/1/nation/20120201201314&sec=nation|title=Perkasa expresses regret over white angpow incident|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503035338/http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2012%2F2%2F1%2Fnation%2F20120201201314&sec=nation|archivedate=2012-05-03|accessdate=2017-09-16}}</ref>。

===稱華人對國家安全構成威脅===
2012年12月12日，土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里表示，馬來西亞華人挑動政治情绪，並指控他們忘記馬來西亞「像天堂」。他亦表示華人社群會對國家安全構成威脅，並指華人如果在經濟上和在政治上權力更大，便會出現類似五一三事件的種族衝突<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/growing-chinese-clout-may-cause-new-may-13-says-ibrahim-ali|title=Growing Chinese clout may cause new May 13, says Ibrahim Ali|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121219105711/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/growing-chinese-clout-may-cause-new-may-13-says-ibrahim-ali/|archivedate=2012-12-19|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

===十字军东征威胁論===
2011年5月12日，土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里表示基督徒推進基督教取代伊斯蘭教成為馬來西亞官方宗教的舉動猶如十字军东征，並批評基督徒不感恩。他亦表示閱讀了《[[马来前锋报|馬來前鋒報]]》布關基督徒打算聯同[[民主行動黨_(馬來西亞)|民主行動黨]]將馬來西亞變成基督教國的新聞後，便打算發動聖戰對付基督徒。民主行動黨回應時批評馬來西亞政府拒絕拘押發表煽动性言論的依布拉欣阿里，證明巫統在背後支持土著權威組織。民主行動黨秘書長[[林冠英|林冠英]]呼籲對依布拉欣所發表的所有言論進行全面調查<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/dap-claims-umno-backing-perkasas-crusade-threat-against-christians|title=DAP Claims UMNO backing Perkasa’s Crusade Threat Against Christians|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107082851/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/dap-claims-umno-backing-perkasas-crusade-threat-against-christians|archivedate=2014-01-07|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

===呼籲焚燒馬來語《聖經》===
2013年1月21日，土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里呼籲焚燒使用「真主」一詞的馬來語《聖經》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2013/01/19/burn-allah-bibles-perkasa-chief-tells-muslims/ |title=Burn "Allah" bibles, Perkasa chief tells Muslims |access-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328032918/http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2013/01/19/burn-allah-bibles-perkasa-chief-tells-muslims/ |archive-date=2016-03-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。被馬來西亞華人公會和馬來西亞印度國民大會黨批評後，依布拉欣阿里又威脅會宣佈停止支持國民陣線。他又表示他無意冒犯基督徒以及煽动种族和宗教紧张局势，但認為焚燒馬來語《聖經》可防止穆斯林受基督教傳福音的影響而轉教。馬來西亞印度國民大會黨領袖[[威尔巴里|威尔巴里]]回應時要求政府懲罰依布拉欣阿里，否則可能會流失非穆斯林選票<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-threatens-to-pull-support-for-mca-mic-over-allah-bible-burning-row|title=Perkasa threatens to pull support for MCA, MIC over Allah bible-burning row|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123221412/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-threatens-to-pull-support-for-mca-mic-over-allah-bible-burning-row|archivedate=2013-01-23|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。依布拉欣阿里其後因其言論涉嫌違反《1948年煽動法令》而被馬來西亞警察調查<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2013/1/25/nation/12623561&sec=nation|title=Perkasa chief being probed over Bible-burning remark|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127072709/http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2013%2F1%2F25%2Fnation%2F12623561&sec=nation|archivedate=2013-01-27|accessdate=2017-09-16}}</ref>。

===貶抑印度教===
2013年3月29日，土著權威組織副主席[[朱基菲諾丁|朱基菲諾丁]]發表貶抑[[印度教|印度教]]的宗教布道，引發信奉印度教的政治人物對其作出批評<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/zul-noordin-asks-why-hindu-gods-did-not-stop-flood/|title=Zul Noordin asks why Hindu gods did not stop flood|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331002238/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/zul-noordin-asks-why-hindu-gods-did-not-stop-flood/|archivedate=2013-03-31|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。[[人民公正黨|人民公正黨]]副主席[[苏仁德兰|苏仁德兰]]要求根據《刑事法法典》第298A段檢控朱基菲諾丁，他又指控朱基菲諾丁是首相[[納吉·阿都拉薩|納吉·阿都拉薩]]的緊密戰友，並認為巫統和國民陣線必须对針對印度教的亵渎言论和嘲讽負上责任<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2013/03/29/charge-insolent-zul-noordin/|title=Charge insolent Zul Noordin|access-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225057/http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2013/03/29/charge-insolent-zul-noordin/|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

馬來西亞印度國民大會黨要求朱基菲諾丁就其針對印度教的貶抑言論道歉。人權組織[[人民之声_(马来西亚组织)|人民之声]]亦怒斥朱基菲，並要求選民在[[2013年馬來西亞大選|2013年大選]]中將他趕出國會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/mic-leaders-tell-zul-noordin-to-shut-up-and-apologise/|title=MIC leaders tell Zul Noordin to ‘shut up’ and apologise|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331002157/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/mic-leaders-tell-zul-noordin-to-shut-up-and-apologise/|archivedate=2013-03-31|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

朱基菲其後在同年4月1日就其言論引發印度人族群不滿致歉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/zulkifli-noordin-apologises-to-indian-community-over-remarks-in-video-clip|title=Zulkifli Noordin apologises to Indian community over remarks in video clip|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130406104340/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/zulkifli-noordin-apologises-to-indian-community-over-remarks-in-video-clip|archivedate=2013-04-06|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>，但1天後，朱基菲被揭發在演說中使用一個對印度人來說極度冒犯的詞彙「[[吉灵|吉灵]]」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/after-hindu-insult-zulkifli-nordin-says-keling/|title=After Hindu insult, Zulkifli Noordin says "Keling"|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130408011908/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/after-hindu-insult-zulkifli-nordin-says-keling|archivedate=2013-04-08|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

===陳平之死===
土著權威組織舉行示威，抗議將[[馬來亞共產黨|馬來亞共產黨]]前總書記[[陳平_(馬來西亞)|陳平]]的遺體運回馬來西亞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-opposes-any-attempt-to-bring-back-chin-pengs-remains|title=Perkasa opposes any attempt to bring back Chin Peng’s remains|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918234150/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-opposes-any-attempt-to-bring-back-chin-pengs-remains|archivedate=2013-09-18|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。 土著權威組織秘書長[[赛哈山|赛哈山]]警告馬华切勿堅持要求馬來西亞政府允許陳平的遺體歸葬馬來西亞，以免使馬來人招惹麻煩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/dont-upset-malays-with-chin-peng-issue-perkasa-warns-mca|title=Don’t upset Malays with Chin Peng issue, Perkasa warns MCA|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923141149/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/dont-upset-malays-with-chin-peng-issue-perkasa-warns-mca|archivedate=2013-09-23|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

===種族騷亂威脅===
土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里警告馬來西亞境內其他種族，如果馬來人仍然維持在貧困水平，國家會發生另一場種族騷亂，並讚賞首相納吉實行土著经济计划是正確的決定，認為它有助提升馬來人的經濟地位。他表示由於馬來人的不滿足導致五一三事件發生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-chief-warns-of-fresh-race-riot-if-malays-not-helped-economically|title=Perkasa chief warns of fresh race riot if Malays not helped economically|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014173540/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/perkasa-chief-warns-of-fresh-race-riot-if-malays-not-helped-economically|archivedate=2013-10-14|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

===查禁馬來語《聖經》===
2013年10月17日，土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里要求馬來西亞政府禁止馬來語《聖經》，認為政府過於對馬來西亞的基督徒妥協，並認為基督徒不滿足，因為他們堅持在《聖經》中使用「真主」一詞。他認為「真主」一詞在馬來西亞只有穆斯林可以使用。他亦認為馬來人已經被「不感恩的基督徒」践踏，要求政府禁止馬來語《聖經》以示報復。他又形容捍衛基督徒使用「真主」一詞的民主行動黨秘書長林冠英是「豬」，並取笑基督徒因為他們的神沒有名字，所以才使用「真主」一詞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2013/10/18/teach-christians-a-lesson-ban-malay-bibles/|title=‘Teach Christians a lesson, ban al-Kitab’|access-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817075126/http://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2013/10/18/teach-christians-a-lesson-ban-malay-bibles/|archive-date=2016-08-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 批評 ==
2010年7月9日，[[美國駐馬來西亞大使|美國駐馬來西亞大使]][[約翰·馬洛特|約翰·馬洛特]]形容土著權威組織是一群「激进分子」<ref>{{cite news |title=What Anwar's Trial Means for Malaysia |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/NA_WSJ_PUB:SB10001424052748704913304575371001840553096.html |publisher=Wall Street Journal |first=John R. |last=Malott |date=2010-07-19 |accessdate=2016-08-09 |archive-date=2012-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110223622/http://online.wsj.com/article/NA_WSJ_PUB:SB10001424052748704913304575371001840553096.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

馬來西亞國會前反對黨領袖、民主行動黨國會領袖[[林吉祥|林吉祥]]表示，土著權威組織利用宗教、種族及民族主義作為手段，但已證明使用這些手段提升及改變馬來人的社會和經濟發展是过时和不相关的<ref>{{cite news |title=Rebirth of a Demon |url=http://blog.limkitsiang.com/2010/03/10/perkasa-rebirth-of-a-demon/ |publisher=Lim Kit Siang |date=2010-03-10 |accessdate=2016-08-09 |archive-date=2010-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619030225/http://blog.limkitsiang.com/2010/03/10/perkasa-rebirth-of-a-demon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[檳城|檳城]][[馬來西亞民政運動黨|民政黨]]官員峇日星指土著權威組織是馬來西亞版本的[[三K黨|三K黨]]，認為它公開提倡种族主义、宗教极端主义和法西斯主义。他又指土著權威組織威脅對基督徒和其他種族和宗教發動聖殿的言論是煽动种族仇恨和社会不和谐。

土著權威組織亦被[[國民陣線|國民陣線]]的兩位華人領袖[[丁福南|丁福南]]和[[罗秋俊|罗秋俊]]形容為「[[種族主義|種族主義者]]」。其後土著權威組織青年團領袖[[阿曼阿扎|阿曼阿扎]]要求兩人道歉。罗秋俊拒絕道歉，並認為土著權威組織的行動是在隔離馬來西亞人。他亦表示，土著權威組織主席依布拉欣阿里在土著權威組織大會上舉起[[馬來短劍|馬來短劍]]的行為是要使馬來西亞內部种族关系變得緊張<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/litee/print/malaysia/No-sorry-for-Perkasa-BN-Chinese-leaders-say/|title=No sorry for Perkasa, BN Chinese leaders say|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130216221233/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/litee/print/malaysia/No-sorry-for-Perkasa-BN-Chinese-leaders-say/|archivedate=2013-02-16|accessdate=2016-08-09}}</ref>。

